ieves, “at the intersection of your experience and mine in a way, I hope, that allows recognition.”  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Sep 2021) 0aAuthorship. 0aSpeculative fictionxHistory and criticism. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Science Fiction & Fantasy.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300262827423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300262827/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles